 <sect1 xml:id="sec-docker-docupdates-sle12-sp3-maint1">
  <title>October 2018 (Maintenance Release of &productname; 12 SP3)</title>
  <!--list of general issues that apply to all books-->
  <xi:include href="common_docupdates_sp3_maint1_i.xml"/>
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Improved consistency of occurrences of &docker; terminology. This
        includes renaming the guide to <citetitle>&deng; Guide</citetitle>.
       </para>
       </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Portus is no longer technical preview only, hence removed
        this sentence from <xref linkend="sec-docker-portus"/> (<link
        xlink:href="&bsc;1098836"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        In <xref
        linkend="sec-docker-sle-images-customizing-the-images-sles11sp4"/>,
        updated the example to &productname; 11 SP4 (<link
        xlink:href="&bsc;1088500"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Using a better suited example for background applications
        (<literal>apache2</literal> rather than <literal>postfix</literal>) in
        <xref linkend="docker-daemons"/> (<link
        xlink:href="&bsc;1084275"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        In <xref linkend="sec-docker-portus"/>, updated the link to the upstream
        Portus documentation and removed the installation procedure, because
        Portus is now provided as a Docker image (<link
        xlink:href="&bsc;1080879"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Switched the example application to create a &docker; container with
        from <systemitem class="daemon">postfix</systemitem> to Apache
        (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1080879"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Corrected the name of pre-built packages for &slea; 12 SP3 in <xref
        linkend="Building-Pre-build-Images"/> (<link
        xlink:href="&bsc;1064156"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         Corrected package name from <package>Portus</package> to
         <package>portus</package> (<link  xlink:href="&bsc;1058365"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         Adjusted names of base images to latest product versions (<link
         xlink:href="&bsc;1050754"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         There is no need to disable copy-on-write for a
         <filename>/var/lib/docker</filename> partition on Btrfs, see <xref
         linkend="Container-Drivers"/> (doc comment #34198).
        </para>
       </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>

